{"tid":44894,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"莫斯科轉機","createTime":"2016-12-18T15:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T15:34:33.000Z","uid":54631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73ad6d0dc0ac8076bf06cb47c27cf3635836b8b8","tid":44894,"uid":54631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:16:18.000Z","msg":"下年一月會經莫斯科轉機去布達佩斯，當地時間下午5點降落，第二日早上11點再飛。<br />\n<br />\n中間有十幾個鐘，所以我諗住出去睇下。有冇巴打都試過轉機出境？我應該點善用呢段時間同埋去邊到好？<br />\n<br />\n而且應該catch尾班車(1am)翻機場瞓好，定搵間酒吧飲下野第二朝先頭班車翻去？"},{"pid":"fab4fed524b088eab0616a2033a09824296219c8","tid":44894,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下年一月會經莫斯科轉機去布達佩斯，當地時間下午5點降落，第二日早上11點再飛。<br />\n<br />\n中間有十幾個鐘，所以我諗住出去睇下。有冇巴打都試過轉機出境？我應該點善用呢段時間同埋去邊到好？<br />\n<br />\n而且應該catch尾班車(1am)翻機場瞓好，定搵間酒吧飲下野第二朝先頭班車翻去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁多時間梗係會入境住一晚，第二朝返都夠時間。<br />\n<br />\n夜晚落紅場行下影相。"},{"pid":"2867ffeb69b3740d058e3fbea54a8f4976728f80","tid":44894,"uid":36565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:42:14.000Z","msg":"kreml 5pm皮已收<br />\n可去睇下夜景 不過而家好凍<br />\nred square, GUM<br />\n機鐵都有半粒鐘一班<br />\n可自己就時間"},{"pid":"10291a370a45d41f68aaac7996638909ff70ee8d","tid":44894,"uid":33242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T10:15:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58e495b4f9de9300524f7cdd86f122c5a6aea2c3","tid":44894,"uid":33242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4caf95518aa9f9481cc9a85727c3e2a2ad2410ea","tid":44894,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T10:19:59.000Z","msg":"七個字，再轉地鐵多三，四個字到紅牆。<br />\n<br />\n個通常好多人都喺地鐵蕩失路。"},{"pid":"a137b81d3e88ba2fd6adad465d200900083fc4f0","tid":44894,"uid":36565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>kreml 5pm皮已收<br />\n可去睇下夜景 不過而家好凍<br />\nred square, GUM<br />\n機鐵都有半粒鐘一班<br />\n可自己就時間</blockquote><br />\n機場去市中心幾耐? 同埋近唔近景點</blockquote><br />\n連埋轉線1粒鐘度 <br />\n市中心就係kreml redsquare gum嗰堆野<br />\n周圍有幾個地鐵站"},{"pid":"0f7798956c9a82e8c7b9764ed3ca26706b04e020","tid":44894,"uid":1666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"試過，又係等十幾個鐘，出左去紅牆玩，仲去左個墓園參觀，不過我係十幾個鐘daytime<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw莫斯科已被蝗攻佔左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6630210834acf07dd745c20517a501b28ad595","tid":44894,"uid":54631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:25:00.000Z","msg":"有咩俄羅斯菜嘅餐廳值得試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52110834e795f3fddf675ec76b828afee4e95b2","tid":44894,"uid":33242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:48:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"560b7892397cb0492e0f15a927faf53a2cbbfe82","tid":44894,"uid":54631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>機場有冇locker 放gip/拎去寄倉先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚拎住咁大個gip出去比人偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行李通常都直寄去目的地，轉機唔駛攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}